604
00:37:45.764 --> 00:37:47.444
I just wanted to hang out with my friends.

605
00:37:50.686 --> 00:37:52.479
I wish that I...

606
00:38:06.660 --> 00:38:09.454
Can I ask you something?

607
00:38:11.206 --> 00:38:12.374
Sure.

608
00:38:14.543 --> 00:38:16.437
Before. you said

609
