754
00:47:55.206 --> 00:47:57.643
All right.

755
00:47:57.667 --> 00:48:00.104
What Tabitha said about people's fears.

756
00:48:00.128 --> 00:48:02.314
their nightmares becoming part
of the forest

757
00:48:02.338 --> 00:48:04.316
