758
00:48:04.340 --> 00:48:06.193
I think it might be. yeah.

759
00:48:06.217 --> 00:48:08.988
"Tip of the spear."

760
00:48:09.012 --> 00:48:10.263
What's that?

761
00:48:11.848 --> 00:48:13.325
This guy named Martin once told me

762
00:48:13.349 --> 00:48:14.952
